Additionally I own an X6 Tablet Ultrabase which docks to the bottom of this
tablet and which extends the functionality to include:

+ (1) serial port
+ (1) parallel port
+ (1) additional VGA port
+ (4) extra USB ports
+ Optical disk drive (MATSHITA UJDA775)
+ (1) additional RJ-11 (telephone) jack
+ (1) additional RJ-45 (ethernet) jack

The tablet functionality has been really nice working with my
[[318ti|BMW_318ti]]. I can fold the computer in half and lay it in the passenger
seat while still on and connected to my OBD-II port in the cabin, scraping
real-time data from the ECU as the car pushes the tachometer through its range.

