The serial port is necessary to access further modules within this E36 unless
one jumps some pins in the 20-pin Pacman connector under the hood. A K+DCAN tool will
do this without needing to jump those pins too. Modules which are inaccessible
are things like the instrument cluster, airbags, ABS + traction control and the
“comfort” features like making headlights flash during key FOB activation and
other small things like this which are programmed with NCSExpert coding.

